Privacy Policy for Open Radio Android Application

At Open Radio, we respect the privacy of our users and are committed to protecting their personal information.
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information in connection with the Open Radio mobile
application (the "App").

Information We Collect.
We collect certain information from you when you use the App, including:

Coarse location: We may collect your approximate region to provide you with local radio stations.
                 This information is only collected with your permission.
Google Analytics: We use Google Analytics to monitor the performance of the App.
                  Google Analytics collects information such as how often users access the App, what pages they visit
                  when they do so, and what other sites they used prior to coming to the App.
                  We use the information we get from Google Analytics only to improve the App.
Internal Images: We store images associated with radio stations internally, in order to provide you with a visual
                 representation of the radio station you are listening to.

Information We Do Not Collect
We do not collect any personal information such as your name, address, or phone number.
We do not persist any information directly.

How We Use Information
We use the information we collect from you to provide and improve the App.
We may also use the information to communicate with you about the App or to offer you promotional offers.
We do not share your information with any third-party vendors, except for Google Analytics.

Data Security
We take reasonable measures to help protect information about you from loss, theft, misuse, and unauthorized access,
disclosure, alteration, and destruction.

Children's Privacy
The App is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information
from children under the age of 13.

Changes to Our Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to make changes to this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes we make will be posted on this page.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at chernyshov.yuriy@gmail.com.

Last Updated: March 22, 2023
